    {
      "id": "detailed_1_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is in poor condition and is being sold as-is, making it an ideal candidate for a dedicated project or for salvageable parts. The engine currently runs roughly and requires significant mechanical attention, and the transmission exhibits noticeable slipping. Externally, the car has multiple large dents, significant paint fading, and visible rust along the rocker panels. The interior shows heavy wear, including several tears in the upholstery and non-functional climate control. Prospective buyers should be prepared for extensive repairs or to use the vehicle for parts.",
